{"tid":1668990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部發言人華春瑩稱中方一向堅決反對竊取智慧財產權","createTime":"2019-10-22T09:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T23:36:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ac463e50fea0cac1fdc2411f8eade80c439f95c7","tid":1668990,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部回應美國國務卿蓬佩奧指，中國政府對美國企業伸出長臂竊取智慧財產權時表示，中方一向堅決反對、亦不感興趣，更不會竊取。<br />\n<br />\n發言人華春瑩表示，長臂管轄是美國依據國內法對外國實體和個人，肆意打壓的單邊制裁工具和霸淩行徑，濫用長臂管轄應該是美方的知識產權。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩引述美中貿委會早前的報告指，97%的受訪美國企業表示在中國市場盈利，74%的中國美國商會成員企業，計劃進一步擴大在華投資，超過95%的企業表示沒有被要求向中國轉讓技術，反問蓬佩奧關於美國企業難以在華有盈利的結論從何而來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1487631_1_L_20191022164733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1487631_1_L_20191022164733.jpg&h=c6d04e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487631-20191022.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487631-20191022.htm&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=fee67d72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487631-20191022.htm&h=b291d6c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487631-20191022.htm</a>"},{"pid":"076093bbb7611397b285ae9ba1de58be694cb18f","tid":1668990,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人"},{"pid":"8c773f74ffa086ceb117255b9f768b1755d8e2c1","tid":1668990,"uid":311198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:53:33.000Z","msg":"A貨強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 